The final restock of 2022 for Large ICE & FROST - head to orea.uk or the link in bio to grab yours! 

-

Making these brewers is quite time-intensive as each unit is post-processed and quality controlled individually. As such, there’s just not much stock around. This restock is the final one for the year for these units and likely there will only be one more release in late January 2023. If you’d like one in time for Christmas - we pack and ship the day after the order is made.

Order early - as supplies are limited and Royal Mail strikes are causing delays to shipments here in the UK.

Get ready to pour it up! 🎉 We're thrilled to announce that coffee content creator and renowned #JerneyPour innovator @jerney will be joining us as a special guest judge for the #ServingCreativityThrowdown. 💚

A couple years back he held one of the coolest photo competitions for coffee content creators we've ever seen, and that's what inspired us to create the Serving Creativity Throwdown!

Jerney is a talented product and brand photographer, using his keen eye for light and shadow to capture stunning images. With a passion for coffee and an eye for artistry, Jerney is the perfect addition to our panel of judges!

Join us in welcoming Jerney to the judging panel!

🗓️ Make sure to mark your calendars for MAY 2nd, when we unveil our top 32 finalists for the Serving Creativity Throwdown! ☕📸

#ICOSABrewhouse #JerneyPour #ServingCreativityThrowdown #CoffeeAdventurer #ICOSAwave

Why did I choose the Lelit Bianca V3? 

There’s a lot of reasons to love this machine. But sometimes technical specifications aren’t as important as the company you’re working with. 
I choose to work with Edika because they wanted a long term relationship and I didn’t feel like another number in their quota. 
Building long term relationships with companies is far beneficial than being paid to do X numbers of reels for X dollars. 

Choose if you can to work more on relationships with companies rather then short term projects. The benefit always outweighs the short term gain.
